source.name: 2007 American Community Survey 1-Year PUMS Population File
source.description: A nationwide survey that collects information such as age, race, income, commute time to work, home value, veteran status, and other data. Data from the American Community Survey and the Puerto Rico Community Survey were collected during calendar year 2007.
